{"tid":458574,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"搵水抱比收兵更仆街","createTime":"2017-11-05T04:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T09:18:27.000Z","uid":58335,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0efaa367110928099e262f0cf0c0c4a287212328","tid":458574,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"收兵已經夠仆街<br />\n但做兵期間,唔多唔少都知自己係兵<br />\n都預左有機會失敗<br />\n<br />\n但如果佢搵你水抱<br />\n你根本唔會知自己係水抱<br />\n你仲滿懷希望終於有男/女朋友<br />\n正當你仲係熱戀期<br />\n點知佢同你講其實佢搵你做水抱,從來冇鍾意過你<br />\n個種就天堂跌落過地獄既感覺真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2783efade2536b352a0c7c0e614fa0cdc039757f","tid":458574,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:54:25.000Z","msg":"抱你老母"},{"pid":"d5eb38ec0499ea61c44c0f419ae3a6956b2bad17","tid":458574,"uid":92836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:58:09.000Z","msg":"水抱仲狗過player"},{"pid":"97641f3fc7489460f7886e7d20a65d93fafe8223","tid":458574,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水抱仲狗過player</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真"},{"pid":"b393dee2865dce3487691162b36cdce868eec1c6","tid":458574,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T08:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5026c24f4db94503be33e84646b1651cec54c0a3","tid":458574,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc31859590911d0dec293ee013ac60d271fa3bc","tid":458574,"uid":136902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:46:22.000Z","msg":"做過兩次水泡，無錫無屌，諗緊女朋友唔比屌無唔係當我水泡？？定唔關事？？"},{"pid":"1741d24b29156427e37a5cf29cac6ae8500d288e","tid":458574,"uid":136902,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做過兩次水泡，無錫無屌，諗緊女朋友唔比屌無唔係當我水泡？？定唔關事？？</blockquote><br />\n係唔係唔比屌，連飛機都唔幫手打，就等於當我係水泡，朋友話係！但我异知係唔係"},{"pid":"89deb38072a8f8e8b05289e3d46a3975987d3ec9","tid":458574,"uid":6031,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:01:08.000Z","msg":"樓上講乜柒"},{"pid":"bdbca689894508f5d63e66489f87cb3e477323ed","tid":458574,"uid":81408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:10:12.000Z","msg":"以為自己出post <br />\n我懂 我做了水泡幾個月<br />\n到最後沉左 佢先講話忘記唔到前度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n傷心到係地鐵喊左出黎"},{"pid":"16cc3411e08a502933408b0aae57908531be56cb","tid":458574,"uid":2781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做過兩次水泡，無錫無屌，諗緊女朋友唔比屌無唔係當我水泡？？定唔關事？？</blockquote><br />\n係唔係唔比屌，連飛機都唔幫手打，就等於當我係水泡，朋友話係！但我异知係唔係</blockquote><br />\n冇得屌頂多係兵咋喎，即係不是男朋友，卻比男朋友更親更重要果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3247aa3a650afb7ab160caf0106c9f16c5b1d3b4","tid":458574,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:16:31.000Z","msg":"睇錯左做水炮，，"},{"pid":"06e7d9f4329531b87864934339a740d7bb340c10","tid":458574,"uid":139613,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯左做水炮，，</blockquote><br />\n做津路真係慘過兵"},{"pid":"db5ae74a6b19c9622e689c91eed8311e819ca209","tid":458574,"uid":18642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:19:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇錯左做水炮，，</blockquote><br />\n做津路真係慘過兵</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e288f20ba0936ea49a81d0e150451cd65038ee6e","tid":458574,"uid":40509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為自己出post <br />\n我懂 我做了水泡幾個月<br />\n到最後沉左 佢先講話忘記唔到前度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n傷心到係地鐵喊左出黎</blockquote><br />\n我以為自己遇到左會賞識自己既伯樂<br />\n但可能只係做左人地水泡<br />\n不過見到佢開心 <br />\n自己都無所謂了<br />\n鐘意一個人 唔一定要得到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926cf036ad9571401f3091c486d05a06d58059b4","tid":458574,"uid":50320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T11:30:01.000Z","msg":"試過一次 X.X"},{"pid":"afef7ddafc937ebf0d802ac9c4c6e5489df0d9e0","tid":458574,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"各取所需姐<br />\n毒撚媾唔到女唔做水泡邊到有閪屌"},{"pid":"c5e62349b62ec6e31d896bb8e6f8a5fd6e3ee96f","tid":458574,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T11:54:37.000Z","msg":"水泡真係最仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d786fe51c98970c1cb611b935d02664aa0ae8a54","tid":458574,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T12:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以為自己出post <br />\n我懂 我做了水泡幾個月<br />\n到最後沉左 佢先講話忘記唔到前度<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n傷心到係地鐵喊左出黎</blockquote><br />\n我以為自己遇到左會賞識自己既伯樂<br />\n但可能只係做左人地水泡<br />\n不過見到佢開心 <br />\n自己都無所謂了<br />\n鐘意一個人 唔一定要得到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好偉大<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">我都係</span>"},{"pid":"76837a388edce5cd158b26dedc59541294d37e2c","tid":458574,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci